# Project Knowledge Base ‚Äî web4-service

This document is the single source of truth for the project's architecture, conventions, and implementation details. Consult it before reading source files.

## Overview

**web4-service** is a pay-per-call AI agent services platform. It exposes HTTP endpoints that AI agents can discover and invoke, with payments handled via the **x402 protocol** (HTTP 402 micropayments in USDC on EVM chains). No API keys are needed ‚Äî clients pay per request through on-chain USDC transfers.

- **Production URL**: `https://web4svc.com` (hosted on Railway)
- **GitHub**: `https://github.com/mapleeit/web4-service`
- **License**: MIT

